review.reviewBody: Pretty tasty! My only complaint is that the 54. Sesame Seed Chicken / 芝麻雞 is sooo dry and chewy - can barely even tell it  chicken. 130. BBQ Pork Fried Rice / 叉燒炒飯d is delicious and a huge portion.
Wow. Finally I found a Chinese food place that I love. To me, this is classic Chinese food like what I grewup on.
Fast delivery,chick chow mien with sweet & sour chicken balls& beef chop suey was good

Hands down this is the best Chinese food in Vancouver. My boyfriend and I cannot get enough of it .

The portions are massive, the quality is always 10/10 and it's perfectly priced. 

There will never be a time where I don't recommend.
Best Chinese food ever and absolutely love their chicken chow mein!  Huge portions. Love love love! Took me 7 years of living here to find my go-to Chinese!!
